Publishing
==========

Before publishing, following files must be updated with the version number:

docs/source/conf.py
    version = 'X.Y.Z'
    release = 'X.Y.Z'

setup.py:
    version='X.Y.Z',
    download_url='https://github.com/gergelyk/pymiscutils/tarball/X.Y.Z',

Relevant git tag must be also created.


Process of publishing:

# push the code
git tag X.Y.Z
git push
git push --tags

# make sure that readthedocs published documentation

# update package
doit build
doit pypi_submit_live

# install package to your machine
sudo pip3 install miscutils --no-cache-dir

